 to higher recall rates and precision on OOV word recognition.\nFurthermore, our proposed combined loss rescaling and weight consolidation\nmethods can support continual learning of an ASR system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2023 02:21:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 09:44:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
