 formation of isolated mildly recycled pulsars with velocity $\\rm\n\\lesssim 360\\,km\\,s^{-1}$ in observations, and such isolated pulsars should\nlocate in the region of pulsars with massive WD companions in the $P_{\\rm\nspin}-\\dot P_{\\rm spin}$ diagram.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2023 11:39:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2023 12:09:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
